                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, D</hi> 125). I took the prisoner at Mr. Sandford's shop—he gave me this shilling—I said, "How many of these have you got?"—she said, "I have got no more"—Mr. Sandford said she was there on the 27th, but she made no answer—Mr. Sandford afterwards brought this other shilling to the station.</p>
